  "title": "ISic003592. Engraved fragment of a sima",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/58RITUTQ\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/58RITUTQ</a></div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<span data-text=\"ρης\">ρης</span>  <span data-text=\"μν\">μν</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/58RITUTQ\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/58RITUTQ</a></div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<span data-text=\"ρης\">ΡΗΣ</span><span data-text=\"μν\">ΜΝ</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text after Frasca 2005</span></span>; </li><li><span class=\"1\">1: <span>Frasca hypothesises: [Ἡ]ρης μν[ημειον]</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>Roughly carved on a fragment of a sima, from the periurban sanctuary attributed to Hera at Scala Portazza.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 60.1012 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a></li><li> 59.1106 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a></li><li> 55.1012bis <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a></li><li> Frasca 2005 143 fig.6 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001441\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001441</a></li><li> Frasca 2009 118 no.7 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001981\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001981</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
